---
// Komponen Proses Kerja Zaidly Agency
---

<section id="process" class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-[#F8F9FA] z-0 hidden lg:block"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center">
      
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 mb-16 lg:mb-0">
        <span class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4 block font-mulish">
          Alur Kerja Kami
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">
          Cara Kami <span class="text-[#7E67F8]">Mewujudkan</span> Website Impian Anda.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 font-mulish leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Proses yang transparan dan terukur untuk memastikan hasil terbaik bagi bisnis UMKM Anda.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-sm font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#7E67F8] transition-all duration-300 font-oswald shadow-lg">
          Mulai Project Sekarang
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 lg:pl-20">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-12 gap-x-10">
          
          <div class="relative">
            <span class="text-6xl font-bold text-slate-100 font-oswald absolute -top-6 -left-4 z-0">01</span>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 font-oswald uppercase">Konsultasi & Strategi</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-mulish leading-relaxed">
                Kami dengarkan kebutuhan bisnis Anda dan susun strategi digital yang paling efektif.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <span class="text-6xl font-bold text-slate-100 font-oswald absolute -top-6 -left-4 z-0">02</span>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 font-oswald uppercase">Desain Kreatif</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-mulish leading-relaxed">
                Pembuatan mockup desain yang modern, responsif, dan mencerminkan brand UMKM Anda.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <span class="text-6xl font-bold text-slate-100 font-oswald absolute -top-6 -left-4 z-0">03</span>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 font-oswald uppercase">Development</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-mulish leading-relaxed">
                Proses coding menggunakan teknologi Astro yang menjamin website Anda super kencang.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <span class="text-6xl font-bold text-slate-100 font-oswald absolute -top-6 -left-4 z-0">04</span>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 font-oswald uppercase">Launch & Support</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-mulish leading-relaxed">
                Website live! Kami berikan panduan pengelolaan dan optimasi SEO agar mulai muncul di Google.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>